======================================================
Test Cases:

Application was tested using a simple linux TFTP client, 'tftp,' using the loopback IP addr 127.0.0.1 PNG image included with source code documents working condition of tftp server under the load of multiple clients. 


======================================================
Architecture:

server was designed to use the concurrency method, each new RRQ from a client would cause the main server app. to fork a child to handle the request.
